    • of

      public static final DefaultGenericArrayType of(GenericArrayType genericArrayType)
      If the supplied GenericArrayType is a DefaultGenericArrayType, returns it; otherwise creates a new DefaultGenericArrayType with the supplied GenericArrayType's generic component type and returns it.
      Parameters:
      genericArrayType - the GenericArrayType to effectively copy (or return); must not be null
      Returns:
      a non-null DefaultGenericArrayType
      Throws:
      NullPointerException - if genericArrayType is null
      Idempotency:
      This method is idempotent but not deterministic (in that it may return a new DefaultGenericArrayType with each invocation).
      Nullability:
      This method never returns null.
      Thread Safety:
      This method is safe for concurrent use by multiple threads.
